Hershel Green positions himself as the group's new leader, declaring himself Emperor of the world.  Rick's final duel with Shane turns out to have cost him severe injuries.  Dr Green saves Rick by grafting farm implements and tools onto his body to replace missing limbs.  As Rick comes to he is told be the green that in his rage he actually killed Lori and their son.  In his grief and anger, he loses his own identity and swears loyalty to Hershel.  It is finally revealed that Hershel Green himself engineered the Zombie apocalypse to take control of the world and rule it with an iron fist, with Rick at his side.  Only Daryl flees, with secret plans for the farm and Rick's newborn son in his care, who will one day grow up to overthrow the Empire that Green has created.
